emini-browser/DESIGN.md:458:- Status code outside 10–69 → `InvalidResponse(\"status code out of range\")`.\nexamples/gemini-browser/DESIGN.md:459:- Missing META after status for 1x/3x (where META is required) →\nexamples/gemini-browser/DESIGN.md:487:### Input status (1x)\nexamples/gemini-browser/DESIGN.md:534:pub struct GeminiResponse { pub status: u8, pub meta: String, pub body: Option<Vec<u8>> }\nexamples/gemini-browser/DESIGN.md:623:| `test_parse_success_header` | `\"20 text/gemini\"` → status 20, meta `\"text/gemini\"` |\nexamples/gemini-browser/DESIGN.md:624:| `test_parse_input_header` | `\"10 Enter your name\"` → status 10, meta `\"Enter your name\"` |\nexamples/gemini-browser/DESIGN.md:625:| `test_parse_redirect_header` | `\"31 gemini://other/path\"` → status 31 |\nexamples/gemini-browser/DESIGN.md:626:| `test_parse_temp_failure` | `\"40 Server busy\"` → status 40 |\nexamples/gemini-browser/DESIGN.md:627:| `test_parse_perm_failure` | `\"51 Not found\"` → status 51 |\nexamples/gemini-browser/DESIGN.md:628:| `test_parse_cert_required` | `\"60 Certificate required\"` → status 60 |\nexamples/gemini-browser/DESIGN.md:629:| `test_parse_empty_meta` | `\"20 \"` → status 20, meta is empty string (or just whitespace trimmed) |\nexamples/gemini-browser/DESIGN.md:630:| `test_parse_meta_no_space` | `\"20\"` with no space → status 20, meta is empty |\nexamples/gemini-browser/DESIGN.md:633:| `test_reject_status_out_of_range` | `\"70 whatever\"` → `InvalidResponse` |\nexamples/gemini-browser/DESIGN.md:634:| `test_reject_status_too_low` | `\"09 whatever\"` → `InvalidResponse` |\nexamples/gemini-browser/prompts/implement.md:16:5. Handle all status code families:\nexamples/gemini-browser/prompts/implement.md:66:    - Test response header parsing (all status families)\nexamples/gemini-browser/prompts/design.md:17:  - Gemini response (status code, meta, body)","numLines":180}}
